ADDIS ABABA, Ethiopia, December 21, 2018/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The U.S. Embassy invites media to Ethiopia Debates! launch program. The Ethiopia Debates! is a nationwide program that creates an important platform for University students to engage in a series of debate competition in which students have the opportunity to learn public speaking skills, and peaceful dialogue and debate techniques.



Ethiopia Debates! will be launched on Saturday December 22, 2018 at 10:00 a.m at the Colonel John C. Robinson American Center, located inside the National Archives and Library Agency (NALA).





You are invited to attend the event at:



Date: Saturday, December 22, 2018 at 10:00a.m

Location: Inside the National Archives and Library Agency (NALA)